A. See, that thou be ſuch a one indeed. But if God hath given thee a new ſpirit, yet thou maiſt ſuffer much; it may be more than thou art willing to ſuffer, before thy afflictions prove beneficial to thee: and God ſaith, that if he ſhall ſpeak concerning a Nation to build and ••
